Oslo is an application for the ATmega328P microcontroller.

Oslo provides a simple file system and a UTC seconds counter.
It is connected to other mpus via the TWI.

To build and install the application :-

  $ make
  $ cd ../bali
  $ avril oslo

To build and install the application and bootloader :-

  connect the ICSP cable between bali and oslo

  $ make image
  $ cd ../bali
  $ (. ./defs.sh && cd ../oslo && make avp)

